org.barghos.math.api.vector

Interface IVec3W

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ITup3fW, ITupfW
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Vec3f

    public interface IVec3W
extends ITup3fW
    This interface grants access to all writing methods of an 3-dimensional float vector.
